{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <h2>最新天文台天氣報告｜未來五天香港天氣預報</h2>\n    <p>天文台展望，明日早上仍然稍涼，驟雨減少。隨後一兩日部分時間有陽光。下週中期天氣不穩定。</p>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>4月24日(五)</cell>\n        <cell>4月25日(六)</cell>\n        <cell>4月26日(日)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>25度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>19度</cell>\n        <cell>21度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>北至東北風4級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東北風4級，離岸間中5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風3至4級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>80-95%</cell>\n        <cell>75-95%</cell>\n        <cell>65-90%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>高</cell>\n        <cell>中低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>多雲，間中有驟雨及幾陣狂風雷暴，雨勢有時頗大。天氣顯著較涼。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，初時有幾陣驟雨。下午短暫時間有陽光。</cell>\n        <cell>部分時間有陽光。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>4月27日(一)</cell>\n        <cell>4月28日(二)</cell>\n        <cell>4月29日(三)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>東至東南風3級。</cell>\n        <cell>東南風3至4級。</cell>\n        <cell>南至東南風4級，高地5級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>65-95%</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n        <cell>75-95%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>中低</cell>\n        <cell>中高</cell>\n        <cell>高</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，日間部分時間有陽光，稍後有幾陣驟雨。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨，局部地區有雷暴。稍後驟雨較多。</cell>\n        <cell>多雲，間中有驟雨及幾陣狂風雷暴。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-23T23:06:16.551378+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":484,"images":0,"source":"GoTrip","fallback":"none"}}